that can calculate
through an electrical interface.

00:17:37.559 --> 00:17:38.526 position:44% line:89% align:start
Hah!

00:17:38.560 --> 00:17:39.861 position:35% line:89% align:start
[clacking]

00:17:39.894 --> 00:17:41.563 position:30% line:89% align:start
[electric zaps]

00:17:41.596 --> 00:17:43.163 position:30% line:89% align:start
