00:17:43.196 --> 00:17:45.767 position:10% line:83% align:start
You certainly are a certified
genius, Jean. Great job!

00:17:51.204 --> 00:17:52.674 position:19% line:83% align:start
And now, a compression
propeller

00:17:52.707 --> 00:17:54.441 position:33% line:83% align:start
that obtains
its propellant force

00:17:54.474 --> 00:17:56.744 position:24% line:83% align:start
by burning jet fuel
in combination with the air.

00:17:56.778 --> 00:17:57.645 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Hah!
-[both] Oh!

00:17:57.679 --> 00:18:00.280 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:18:00.314 --> 00:18:02.884 position:30% line:83% align:start
Now presenting
a laminated integrated circuit

00:18:02.917 --> 00:18:05.520 position:16% line:83% align:start
