waves from space.

00:18:22.436 --> 00:18:24.237 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Ah ha!
-[both gasp]

00:18:25.673 --> 00:18:27.575 position:30% line:89% align:start
[both] Amazing.

00:18:27.609 --> 00:18:30.444 position:10% line:83% align:start
