a graphite channel heart

00:18:32.312 --> 00:18:33.915 position:35% line:83% align:start
that works
through isotope reaction.

00:18:33.948 --> 00:18:35.315 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Whoa!
-[Nadia] Wow!

00:18:36.450 --> 00:18:40.120 position:10% line:83% align:start
Get ready, my next invention
will turn night into day.

00:18:41.956 --> 00:18:44.291 position:33% line:83% align:start
-[explosion]
-[Marie and Nadia gasp]

00:18:47.629 --> 00:18:49.564 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's incredible, Jean.

00:18:49.597 --> 00:18:52.867 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'd say you were a genius
but you're so much more!

00:18:52.900 --> 00:18:55.302 position:16% line:89% align:start
Right. That's what I am.

00:18:55.903 --> 00:19:00.140 position:38% line:89% align:start
A genius!

00:19:01.743 --> 00:19:04.779 position:27% line:89% align:start
[birds chirping]

00:19:08.883 --> 00:19:11.786 position:27% line:83% align:start
Now, the gateway
to your homeland.

00:19:13.487 --> 00:19:14.922 position:27% line:89% align:start
What do you mean?

00:19:15.523 --> 00:19:17.892 position:27% line:83% align:start
Your long awaited
journey begins now.

00:19:17.925 --> 00:19:21.161 position:35% line:89% align:start
[whirring]

00:19:26.000 --> 00:19:29.236 position:16% line:89% align:start
[dramatic music playing]

00:19:58.833 --> 00:20:01.903 position:19% line:83% align:start
Etoile de la Seine 10,
you may launch on my mark.

00:20:11.879 --> 00:20:14.916 position:10% line:83% align:start
Jean, have I told you lately
that you're a certified genius?

00:20:14.949 --> 00:20:18.586 position:7% line:83% align:start
Setting autopilot, destination:
the African continent.

00:20:18.619 --> 00:20:21.254 position:30% line:83% align:start
I can't believe
this is actually happening!

00:20:21.288 --> 00:20:22.489 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is a dream come true.

00:20:22.523 --> 00:20:24.826 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Thanks.
-Oh. You are wrong, Nadia.

00:20:24.859 --> 00:20:26.259 position:13% line:89% align:start
This is actually my dream.

00:20:28.730 --> 00:20:30.698 position:13% line:89% align:start
Where did King run off to?

00:20:30.732 --> 00:20:33.034 position:21% line:83% align:start
He's still performing
in the circus in France.

00:20:33.067 --> 00:20:34.736 position:33% line:89% align:start
No, he isn't.

00:20:34.769 --> 00:20:36.704 position:19% line:83% align:start
We must have forgotten
him back on the island.

00:20:36.738 --> 00:20:38.405 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, Jean.

00:20:38.438 --> 00:20:39.741 position:13% line:83% align:start
We have to turn this thing
around

00:20:39.774 --> 00:20:41.042 position:10% line:89% align:start
and bring King back with us.

00:20:41.075 --> 00:20:44.377 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm afraid it's too late
to turn around now, Nadia.

00:20:44.411 --> 00:20:46.581 position:24% line:89% align:start
We're on autopilot.

00:20:46.614 --> 00:20:48.716 position:30% line:83% align:start
But we have to
go back and get him.

00:20:48.750 --> 00:20:50.685 position:13% line:89% align:start
I'm really sorry about this

00:20:50.718 --> 00:20:53.054 position:24% line:83% align:start
but we can't cancel
the journey once it's begun.

00:20:53.087 --> 00:20:55.790 position:24% line:83% align:start
Well then, I guess
I'll just have to do it myself.

00:20:55.823 --> 00:20:58.358 position:35% line:83% align:start
-[clacking]
-Hey, don't you touch that.

00:20:58.391 --> 00:21:00.327 position:35% line:83% align:start
-That's...
-[beeping]

00:21:00.360 --> 00:21:03.030 position:7% line:89% align:start
...the self-destruct apparatus!

00:21:03.064 --> 00:21:04.565 position:38% line:89% align:start
[zapping]

00:21:04.599 --> 00:21:07.502 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Jean] It sets off
a gunpowder charge!

00:21:07.535 --> 00:21:09.003 position:35% line:89% align:start
[explosion]

00:21:18.112 --> 00:21:19.312 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Where am I?

00:21:20.548 --> 00:21:21.414 position:38% line:89% align:start
My ship.

00:21:22.717 --> 00:21:24.652 position:33% line:89% align:start
Nadia. Marie.

00:21:26.854 --> 00:21:29.624 position:33% line:83% align:start
My invention
was a failure after all.

00:21:30.490 --> 00:21:31.926 position:27% line:89% align:start
Why did it fail?

00:21:32.994 --> 00:21:35.630 position:16% line:89% align:start
I always fail. I guess--

00:21:35.663 --> 00:21:37.565 position:13% line:89% align:start
[Nemo] Don't ever give up.

00:21:37.598 --> 00:21:40.835 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Captain Nemo! It's you.

00:21:40.868 --> 00:21:43.938 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Nemo] Today's mistake
is tomorrow's breakthrough.

00:21:43.971 --> 00:21:48.408 position:7% line:83% align:start
Develop your capacities with a
strong will and sense of belief.

00:21:50.443 --> 00:21:51.679 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Jean] Captain.

00:21:52.046 --> 00:21:54.982 position:5% line:89% align:start
[Nemo] Genius is 1% inspiration,

00:21:55.016 --> 00:21:57.618 position:27% line:89% align:start
99% perspiration.

00:22:00.087 --> 00:22:02.455 position:19% line:89% align:start
Those words were spoken

00:22:02.489 --> 00:22:05.026 position:7% line:83% align:start
by the great American inventor
Thomas Edison.

00:22:07.962 --> 00:22:12.332 position:16% line:83% align:start
Remember those words and
make Nadia's dream come true.

00:22:13.400 --> 00:22:15.368 position:21% line:89% align:start
Wait, Commander Nemo.

00:22:15.402 --> 00:22:18.639 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Nemo] Don't call me commander.

00:22:19.607 --> 00:22:23.443 position:38% line:89% align:start
Captain!

00:22:24.879 --> 00:22:26.547 position:33% line:89% align:start
Captain Nemo!

00:22:27.949 --> 00:22:29.016 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:22:34.421 --> 00:22:36.456 position:19% line:89% align:start
Oh, I-- it was a dream.

00:22:37.158 --> 00:22:38.526 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:22:38.559 --> 00:22:41.696 position:24% line:89% align:start
[waterfall gushing]

00:22:41.729 --> 00:22:42.563 position:44% line:89% align:start
King!

00:22:46.000 --> 00:22:47.768 position:41% line:83% align:start
[Marie]
King must have gotten jealous.

00:22:47.802 --> 00:22:49.670 position:10% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] Why do you think so?

00:22:49.704 --> 00:22:52.707 position:16% line:83% align:start
Because of you and Jean.
He probably felt left out.

00:22:52.740 --> 00:22:54.575 position:24% line:89% align:start
You think he knows?

00:22:54.609 --> 00:22:56.409 position:35% line:83% align:start
Of course,
he does. He's all-knowing.

00:22:58.679 --> 00:23:00.882 position:30% line:83% align:start
So do you think
you're in love with Jean?

00:23:01.916 --> 00:23:03.150 position:33% line:89% align:start
I don't know.

